320
00:19:30,100 --> 00:19:31,420
You're about to be discharged.

321
00:19:32,271 --> 00:19:33,260
I came to take you home.

322
00:19:41,093 --> 00:19:42,660
I'm not going back to Blue Blade.

323
00:20:17,940 --> 00:20:18,740
I'm sorry.

324
00:20:21,300 --> 00:20:22,900
Don't apologize to me.

325
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:25,980
When you came

326
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:27,740
with the Brigadier,

327
00:20:27,740 --> 00:20:29,820
I told you right then
it wasn't your fault.

328
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:33,100
Brigadier even joked

329
00:20:34,820 --> 00:20:36,820
that I, as his best shooter, was broken.

330
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:40,700
Yeah, that's right.

331
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:43,500
But I wasn't the best one.

332
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:45,180
At Blue Blade,

333
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:46,540
we never run out of great snipers.

334
00:20:48,220 --> 00:20:48,980
Yi Nanwang

335
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:51,260
will be better than me.

336
00:21:06,540 --> 00:21:07,460
It's okay.

337
00:21:09,020 --> 00:21:10,220
Even if you're not a sniper,

338
00:21:10,220 --> 00:21:11,500
you can still be a great soldier.

339
00:21:18,660 --> 00:21:19,740
Don't blame yourself.

340
00:21:20,780 --> 00:21:21,740
I have no regrets.

341
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:23,580
If I had to do it again,

342
00:21:24,420 --> 00:21:26,020
I'd still charge forward.

343
00:21:28,820 --> 00:21:29,980
Even if one day

344
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:32,500
I completely lose my sight,

345
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:35,020
I promise I'll live well.

346
00:21:37,580 --> 00:21:38,580
You know,

347
00:21:40,060 --> 00:21:42,020
Ke'er joined the military because of me.

348
00:21:42,420 --> 00:21:43,500
But all these years,

349
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:44,940
I haven't really treated her right.

350
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:48,740
Now she's retiring.

351
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:52,180
I want to take her home myself.

352
00:21:53,220 --> 00:21:54,980
My eyesight's going to get worse.

353
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:58,020
So while I can still see,

354
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,220
I want to spend more time with her

355
00:22:00,220 --> 00:22:01,382
like a normal boyfriend.

356
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:06,980
I can't be watching you two
be sweet every day, can I?

357
00:22:17,460 --> 00:22:18,220
Sir.

358
00:22:19,820 --> 00:22:21,740
Lieutenant Cheng Yuan,
Blue Blade Special Ops.

359
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:27,500
I request to leave active duty.

360
00:22:29,020 --> 00:22:30,300
Requesting official approval.

361
00:22:34,660 --> 00:22:36,500
(Navy)

362
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:08,540
(Cheng Yuan)

363
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:55,660
(People's Liberation Army Navy)

364
00:23:57,140 --> 00:24:00,460
(Chinese People's Liberation Army)

365
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:13,220
(First Place,
International Sniper Competition)

366
00:24:16,740 --> 00:24:17,500
You're leaving.

367
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:21,100
I know you want to say goodbye.

368
00:24:23,820 --> 00:24:25,900
(First Place,
International Sniper Competition)

369
00:24:34,740 --> 00:24:36,420
I should've visited sooner.

370
00:24:36,780 --> 00:24:38,740
You're the first one
to win back the Tai'e Sword.

371
00:24:41,220 --> 00:24:42,740
Sign your name in the guest book.

372
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,060
Yes, Sir.

373
00:24:56,020 --> 00:24:58,260
