397
00:27:03,671 --> 00:27:05,020
You don't need to remind me.

398
00:27:38,060 --> 00:27:38,900
Cheng Yuan.

399
00:27:40,740 --> 00:27:42,460
Lieutenant, Blue Blade Special Ops Team.

400
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:45,300
Eight years of service.

401
00:27:46,220 --> 00:27:47,340
You are hereby approved

402
00:27:47,426 --> 00:27:48,915
to retire from active duty

403
00:27:49,500 --> 00:27:50,700
as of today.

404
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:52,740
Yes, Sir.

405
