440
00:29:22,300 --> 00:29:23,020
No, please.

441
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:24,540
That would look bad.

442
00:29:24,940 --> 00:29:26,260
What's bad about it?

443
00:29:26,260 --> 00:29:27,340
You're not in an army.

444
00:29:27,740 --> 00:29:29,020
What is it about?

445
00:29:29,820 --> 00:29:32,500
Dad, Mom wants to give me
special treatment.

446
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:33,540
Talk some sense into her.

447
00:29:33,700 --> 00:29:34,940
That's not okay.

448
00:29:34,980 --> 00:29:36,700
Special meals are favoritism.

449
00:29:38,260 --> 00:29:39,500
Seriously?

450
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:41,020
I can't stand you two.

451
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:42,540
You're both model employees.

452
00:29:42,540 --> 00:29:43,260
Just eat already.

453
00:29:44,820 --> 00:29:47,060
Zong Qing's heading off
for training for a few days.

454
00:29:47,060 --> 00:29:48,180
Have you two talked?

455
00:29:49,220 --> 00:29:51,300
Yeah, he told me.

456
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:53,740
I don't ask much about what he's doing.

457
00:29:54,020 --> 00:29:56,020
I just stay home
and wait for him to come back.

458
00:29:59,260 --> 00:30:00,260
I'm done, Mom.

459
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:01,300
I'm heading to work.

460
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:04,700
There is one bite left! Finish it.

461
00:30:04,700 --> 00:30:05,420
No thanks.

462
00:30:05,420 --> 00:30:06,226
Dad, I'm off.

463
00:30:06,226 --> 00:30:07,780
Even if you're busy, you should eat up.

464
00:30:07,980 --> 00:30:08,540
Your health...

465
00:30:08,540 --> 00:30:10,540
It's my capital for life.

466
00:30:11,780 --> 00:30:12,740
Thanks for the pep talk.

467
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:13,940
